### ================================================================
### ORD Agent Discovery → A2A Communication
###
### Prerequisites: run demo/demo.sh
### ================================================================

@spaceship = http://localhost:3001
@commander = http://localhost:3002
@ordProviderSuper = http://localhost:3004

### ================================================================
### Part 1: ORD Discovery
### ================================================================

### Step 1: ORD well-known entry point

# @name ordWellKnown
GET {{spaceship}}/.well-known/open-resource-discovery
Accept: application/json

### Step 2: ORD document — lists agents, apiResources, entityTypes

@ordDocPath = {{ordWellKnown.response.body.openResourceDiscoveryV1.documents[0].url}}

# @name ordDocument
GET {{spaceship}}{{ordDocPath}}
Accept: application/json

### ================================================================
### Part 2: Super Agent ORD Discovery
### ================================================================

### Step 3: Super Agent ORD well-known entry point

# @name ordWellKnownSuper
GET {{ordProviderSuper}}/.well-known/open-resource-discovery
Accept: application/json

### Step 4: Super Agent ORD document — the commander agent

@ordDocPathSuper = {{ordWellKnownSuper.response.body.openResourceDiscoveryV1.documents[0].url}}

# @name ordDocumentSuper
GET {{ordProviderSuper}}{{ordDocPathSuper}}
Accept: application/json

### ================================================================
### Part 3: Agent Card → A2A Call
### ================================================================

### Step 5: Fetch Repair Technician agent card

# @name repairCard
GET {{spaceship}}/repair/agent.json
Accept: application/json

### Step 6: Call Repair agent — "The engines are overheating!"

POST {{spaceship}}/repair
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "message/send",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [{"kind": "text", "text": "The engines are overheating!"}],
      "messageId": "demo-msg-1"
    }
  }
}

### Step 7: Fetch Solar Explorer agent card

# @name solarCard
GET {{spaceship}}/solar/agent.json
Accept: application/json

### Step 8: Call Solar agent — "What's the weather like on Jupiter?"

POST {{spaceship}}/solar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "message/send",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [{"kind": "text", "text": "What's the weather like on Jupiter?"}],
      "messageId": "demo-msg-2"
    }
  }
}

### ================================================================
### Part 4: Commander — Automated ORD → A2A
###
### The commander reads ORD, discovers crew agents, delegates via A2A.
### ================================================================

### Step 9: Commander agent card

# @name commanderCard
GET {{commander}}/.well-known/agent.json
Accept: application/json

### Step 10: Ask commander to handle a repair emergency

POST {{commander}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "message/send",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [{"kind": "text", "text": "Hull breach on deck 3! Shields are failing!"}],
      "messageId": "demo-msg-3"
    }
  }
}

### Step 11: Ask commander a navigation question

POST {{commander}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 4,
  "method": "message/send",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [{"kind": "text", "text": "What's the weather on Mars? Can we land safely?"}],
      "messageId": "demo-msg-4"
    }
  }
}

### ================================================================
### Part 5: A2A Editor Playground
###
### Try the full story in the visual A2A Editor:
###   https://open-resource-discovery.github.io/a2a-editor/playground
###
### 1. Click "+ Add" and enter:  http://localhost:3001/repair
### 2. Send: "The warp drive is making strange noises!"
### 3. Add another agent:        http://localhost:3001/solar
### 4. Send: "Tell me a fun fact about Saturn's rings"
### 5. Add the commander:        http://localhost:3002
### 6. Send: "We need to land on Mars, check the weather first!"
###    → Watch the commander discover agents via ORD and delegate.
### ================================================================